comments.body:
This call might cause a side effect that is considered unwanted, no?

Here is an [analogous code:](https://code.woboq.org/qt5/qtbase/src/widgets/widgets/qlineedit.cpp.html#_ZN9QLineEdit12setValidatorEPK10QValidator):
```
void QLineEdit::setValidator(const QValidator *v)
{
    Q_D(QLineEdit);
    d->control->setValidator(v);
}
```
I'd leave `setCheckValidator()` function untouched.

